{"tid":524113,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登真係一個思想充滿矛盾既地方","createTime":"2018-01-09T09:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T06:28:25.000Z","uid":67407,"like":220,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd436f1cc3f4d2a86c8595e791c72cbe8655c10","tid":524113,"uid":67407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:05:46.000Z","msg":"見到有關大陸人正面新聞一定負評，見人死人冧樓就一定正評，對於支那人既仇恨我明白，但若果個內容有關張敬軒/黎明就一定正評。<br />\n<br />\n陳小春話愛國、翻大陸搵錢就係奶共。Beyond、梅姐唱愛國歌就係集體回憶，周潤發就提都無人提。<br />\n<br />\n一個又廢又窮既男人比有錢仔搶左條女，之後發𡚒圖強，事業拍得住有錢仔，我諗好多連登仔都會好欣賞，除左陳偉霆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所有女人都係雞，係港女，但日日叫春無女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baff17bef1080d4ef6a8151f982cb55c0616e452","tid":524113,"uid":67407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbaf7d0f237f4bcbabfe7b2b8e534f8411d0c17","tid":524113,"uid":50779,"like":28,"dislike":30,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:09:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70b048ce72f3995f82ea9e4c60d57863c3a00f16","tid":524113,"uid":9726,"like":81,"dislike":5,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:12:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"060198110a565f2214c51722fffc4859797654f1","tid":524113,"uid":65780,"like":28,"dislike":5,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"所以我成日話抵啲毒撚冇女嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d927b7979256b0b5ac6772157bb9fe5565b1c36","tid":524113,"uid":47359,"like":40,"dislike":3,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:32:11.000Z","msg":"連登得一個人?"},{"pid":"ac22a030e8acebcc5d3b48898596655b7558f9ec","tid":524113,"uid":67407,"like":24,"dislike":20,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"問連登係咪得一個人/係咪要令連登一言堂既人係咪無睇清楚Topic同內文，而家講緊係連登唔少人思想矛盾邏輯混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d9d5ad948717fa4d307d5c7d2603e6b79c2108","tid":524113,"uid":20914,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T10:06:07.000Z","msg":"幾批唔同人嚟，講嘅嘢唔同有咩咁出奇"},{"pid":"adf8dbe6759876a41d263bb0e2c06f6c7bc3cb96","tid":524113,"uid":62424,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"唔好咁認真啦 屌<br />\n你屌佢地都無用架啦 哂氣啦"},{"pid":"15fc477479b1971ae00d21b1b906fd596cc2f151","tid":524113,"uid":133502,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T10:08:34.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得的士陳個故事幾勵志"},{"pid":"5110d527da0075e4ceae61091a6418d58bbfcfe2","tid":524113,"uid":67407,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾批唔同人嚟，講嘅嘢唔同有咩咁出奇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係，如果真係存在幾批人，咁點解呢d post既正評/負評/留言態度係壓倒性？係咪代表另一批唔同意見既人連正負評都唔敢？"},{"pid":"08c818466232b78a3847de6990bf90158fa39455","tid":524113,"uid":67407,"like":44,"dislike":8,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T10:20:18.000Z","msg":"仲有，不嬲連登思想不嬲大一統架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政見：必定要係港獨<br />\n<br />\n新聞：女人比人強姦一定係女錯<br />\n<br />\n種族：中國人（除左某幾個）一定係抵死、南亞或似南亞人既人（除左喬寶寶）都應該送死"},{"pid":"272a277ac20c3e9d82b7b9b796e7b8957ee263a1","tid":524113,"uid":67407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5818cdd94906f74b17c519e126449baf9cadaf31","tid":524113,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9dbaf7d0f237f4bcbabfe7b2b8e534f8411d0c17","tid":524113,"uid":50779,"like":28,"dislike":30,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:09:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"似?<br />\n<br />\n香港間間茶餐廳部部電視機都長開播住TVB 算唔算統一左思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793c333b915552e235eb1c4d33ce30a8aadf12c9","tid":524113,"uid":